fields.title: Design Patient Registration Module
fields.description: Design the front-end and back-end for the patient registration module, including validation and storage of patient data.

fields.title: Implement Appointment Scheduling
fields.description: Develop the appointment scheduling feature, including calendar integration and reminders

fields.title: User Authentication and Authorization
fields.description: Implement user authentication and authorization using secure protocols

fields.title: Set Up Billing System
fields.description: Create the billing system for handling patient invoices and payment processing.

fields.title: Implement Interactive Maps
fields.description: Develop an interactive map feature that shows the location of listed properties with filterable markers.

fields.title: Integrate Property Search Functionality
fields.description: Integrate search functionality that allows users to search for properties based on price, location, and other filters.

fields.title: Set Up Database for Property Listings
fields.description: Set up and configure the database to store property listings, images, and user information.

fields.title: Implement Patient Login System
fields.description: creating the backend to handle patient authentication, implementing secure password storage, and integrating the login form with the frontend. The system should allow patients to securely log in, manage sessions, and recover forgotten passwords
